Package: BayesCNet
Type: Package
Title: Hierarchical Bayesian Inference of Cell Type-Specific Regulatory Networks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Fengdi", "Zhao", email = "fengdizhao@ufl.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: A hierarchical Bayesian framework for inferring cell type-specific 
    gene regulatory networks from single-cell multi-omics data. Leverages cell 
    type relationships to improve network accuracy, especially for rare cell 
    populations.
